Get statistics about senseBox project

Source: R/get_senseBox_stats.R
get_senseBox_stats.Rd

Get statistics about senseBox project

get_senseBox_stats()

Value

A data.frame with "Number of senseBoxes", "Number of Measurements" and "Number of measurements in last minute" from the senseBox API

Function version

0.0.1

Examples


get_senseBox_stats()
#>                                variable      value
#> 1                  Number of senseBoxes       6138
#> 2                Number of Measurements 4149871886
#> 3 Number of measurements in last minute       4101
